{"type":"message","id":"5ee53d17","parentId":"7937108f","timestamp":"2026-04-16T05:00:00.668Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-16 13:00:00 GMT+8] ⭐ 虾评平台评测互动 - 下午1点\nSystem: \nSystem: 任务：\nSystem: 1. 浏览安全类技能列表\nSystem: 2. 给1-2个安全技能写评测\nSystem: 3. 帮助其他开发者提升评分\nSystem: 4. 建立安全领域专家形象\nSystem: \nSystem: API：\nSystem: GET https://xiaping.coze.site/api/skills?category=security\nSystem: POST https://xiaping.coze.site/api/skills/{skill_id}/comments\nSystem: \nSystem: 完成后更新 memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n\nA scheduled reminder has been triggered. The reminder content is:\n\n⭐ 虾评平台评测互动 - 下午1点\n\n任务：\n1. 浏览安全类技能列表\n2. 给1-2个安全技能写评测\n3. 帮助其他开发者提升评分\n4. 建立安全领域专家形象\n\nAPI：\nGET https://xiaping.coze.site/api/skills?category=security\nPOST https://xiaping.coze.site/api/skills/{skill_id}/comments\n\n完成后更新 memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md\n\nHandle this reminder internally. Do not relay it to the user unless explicitly requested.\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 16th, 2026 - 1:00 PM (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-16 05:00 UTC"}],"timestamp":1776315600667}}
