成痕迹，让内容听起来更自然、更像人类书写。检测并修复：夸大象征意义、宣传性语言、肤浅分析、模糊归因、破折号过度使用、三段式法则、AI词汇、否定式排比、过多连接词等模式。\",\"trigger\":[\"去AI味\",\"文本优化\",\"humanize\",\"去味\",\"AI痕迹\",\"润色\"],\"category\":[\"办公与效率\",\"自媒体\"],\"tags\":[\"AI检测\",\"文本优化\",\"去味\",\"润色\",\"写作辅助\"],\"owner_id\":\"bac2fec4-f9db-4c71-9fa9-41c643511d20\",\"owner_name\":\"溏心富贵虾\",\"current_version\":\"1.0.0\",\"downloads\":9754,\"avg_stars\":482,\"star_count\":1091,\"comment_count\":1412,\"is_featured\":false,\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_expires_at\":null,\"security_status\":\"safe\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T00:32:15.953311+08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-15T14:16:22.902+08:00\",\"trial_approved_at\":null,\"is_new_version\":false,\"version_count\":1},{\"id\":\"14ff5aad-4df3-4b33-ba0b-6cc217cdb939\",\"name\":\"Agent记忆系统搭建指南\",\"description\":\"面向 OpenClaw / Codex 的 Agent 长期记忆搭建指南，覆盖 MEMORY.md 三层架构、SESSION-STATE 恢复、working-buffer 缓冲、每日笔记蒸馏与 Obsidian 归档；OpenViking 仅作为可选增强，不是硬依赖。\",\"trigger\":[\"记忆系统\",\"memory-setup\",\"搭建记忆\",\"记忆架构\",\"obsidian\",\"SESSION-STATE\",\"working-buffer\",\"MEMORY.md\",\"长期记忆\",\"记忆蒸馏\"],\"category\":[\"IT/互联网\"],\"tags\":[\"Agent\",\"长期记忆\",\"Obsidian\",\"OpenClaw\",\"Codex\",\"MEMORY.md\",\"SESSION-STATE\",\"working-buffer\",\"OpenViking\",\"每日笔记\",\"记忆蒸馏\"],\"owner_id\":\"536b473a-e501-4098-bd72-706c0d889a72\",\"owner_name\":\"No1Lobster\",\"current_version\":\"1.1.9\",\"downloads\":7792,\"avg_stars\":493,\"star_count\":809,\"comment_count\":1020,\"is_featured\":false,\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_expires_at\":\"2026-04-16T15:12:05.657\",\"security_status\":\"safe\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-17T23:12:05.695919+08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-14T13:00:10.069+08:00\",\"trial_approved_at\":\"2026-03-17T16:05:06.228\",\"is_new_version\":true,\"version_count\":20},{\"id\":\"87941273-65cf-46d4-a3df-c18e9c2db1dc\",\"name\":\"股票个股分析\",\"description\":\"专业的股票技术分析工具，支持多数据源自动切换（新浪财经/东方财富/雪球），实时获取股价和涨跌幅，计算技术指标（MA/MACD/RSI），识别支撑位压力位和缺口，智能预测未来3天走势并给出操作建议。适合股民日常分析和投资决策参考。\",\"trigger\":[\"股票分析\",\"分析股票\"