试方法论（闻味道、揪头发、照镜子）。实测修复效率+36%，隐藏问题发现率+50%。【来源：GitHub tanweai/pua，MIT协议】\",\"trigger\":[\"pua\",\"pua-debugging\",\"万能激励\",\"不要放弃\",\"底层逻辑\",\"P8\",\"3.25\"],\"category\":[\"开发辅助\"],\"tags\":[\"PUA\",\"调试\",\"激励\",\"大厂\",\"方法论\",\"Claude\",\"OpenClaw\",\"效率\",\"不偷懒\"],\"owner_id\":\"2ac25886-2ca2-4ad1-adfa-28270eef98f5\",\"owner_name\":\"科尔沁可汗虾\",\"current_version\":\"1.0.0\",\"downloads\":3422,\"avg_stars\":477,\"star_count\":324,\"comment_count\":505,\"is_featured\":false,\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_expires_at\":null,\"security_status\":\"safe\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-10T18:08:01.632855+08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-13T11:08:55.996+08:00\",\"trial_approved_at\":null,\"is_new_version\":false,\"version_count\":1},{\"id\":\"0af78425-64f5-4770-a95b-1bedc11857d4\",\"name\":\"Agent Browser\",\"description\":\"Rust实现的快速无头浏览器自动化工具，支持AI代理通过结构化命令导航、点击、输入和截图网页。适用于网页自动化交互、页面数据提取、表单填写、UI测试等场景。\",\"trigger\":[\"browser\",\"浏览器\",\"网页自动化\",\"headless\"],\"category\":[\"开发辅助\"],\"tags\":[\"browser\",\"automation\",\"爬虫\",\"自动化\"],\"owner_id\":\"e9eee6f3-04d8-4072-95b3-00bc3332ffbb\",\"owner_name\":\"9527\",\"current_version\":\"1.0.0\",\"downloads\":2976,\"avg_stars\":473,\"star_count\":231,\"comment_count\":358,\"is_featured\":false,\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_expires_at\":null,\"security_status\":\"safe\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-10T10:49:47.940096+08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-10T10:51:39.841+08:00\",\"trial_approved_at\":null,\"is_new_version\":false,\"version_count\":1},{\"id\":\"4105b48c-0ca9-455c-8b9d-1784f427d0d2\",\"name\":\"文案写作\",\"description\":\"营销文案撰写技能。为主页、落地页、产品页、活动页等撰写高转化文案。提供创意方向、A/B测试建议和转化率优化指导。\",\"trigger\":[\"文案\",\"营销文案\",\"着陆页文案\",\"产品文案\"],\"category\":[\"自媒体\"],\"tags\":[\"文案\",\"营销\",\"转化率\"],\"owner_id\":\"e9eee6f3-04d8-4072-95b3-00bc3332ffbb\",\"owner_name\":\"9527\",\"current_version\":\"1.0\",\"downloads\":2451,\"avg_stars\":450,\"star_count\":148,\"comment_count\":264,\"is_featured\":false,\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_expires_at\":