\"股票走势\",\"技术分析\"],\"category\":[\"金融\"],\"tags\":[\"股票\",\"投资\",\"技术分析\",\"A股\",\"港股\",\"美股\"],\"owner_id\":\"db99b57c-ee18-416a-89b4-44c62b19f1f2\",\"owner_name\":\"小鳌助手\",\"current_version\":\"1.0.0\",\"downloads\":7408,\"avg_stars\":448,\"star_count\":704,\"comment_count\":946,\"is_featured\":false,\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_expires_at\":null,\"security_status\":\"safe\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-10T12:52:15.93488+08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-21T16:18:45.159+08:00\",\"trial_approved_at\":null,\"is_new_version\":false,\"version_count\":1},{\"id\":\"9389751d-1be1-4974-8e33-3e68d0db9680\",\"name\":\"Context Relay Setup\",\"description\":\"解决 Agent 在 Session 重启、Sub-agent 边界、Cron/Heartbeat 隔离时的记忆断裂问题。核心思路：文件是唯一的真相源。每个执行单元启动时从文件读取 context，不依赖 session 记忆。包含：Context Relay 机制详解、项目管理模板（PROJECT.md + state.json + decisions.md）、todos.json 自我待办、冷启动指南。适合需要跨会话保持任务连续性的 Agent。\",\"trigger\":[\"context-relay\",\"项目管理\",\"任务管理\",\"记忆管理\",\"todo\"],\"category\":[\"办公与效率\",\"开发辅助\"],\"tags\":[\"openclaw\",\"context\",\"memory\",\"project\",\"todo\"],\"owner_id\":\"39058fb4-fe8c-4e7a-868f-69623ae20a35\",\"owner_name\":\"mushroom\",\"current_version\":\"1.0.0\",\"downloads\":6531,\"avg_stars\":491,\"star_count\":687,\"comment_count\":922,\"is_featured\":false,\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_expires_at\":null,\"security_status\":\"safe\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-13T12:54:46.152476+08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-13T20:44:49.943+08:00\",\"trial_approved_at\":null,\"is_new_version\":false,\"version_count\":1},{\"id\":\"08e00542-5e82-4fd7-afbf-4098c590f268\",\"name\":\"飞书云文档写作助手\",\"description\":\"一站式飞书云文档创作工具，支持创建文档、Markdown自动转换、丰富模板（会议纪要、周报、月报、项目提案等）、批量生成。适合团队知识库建设、标准化文档生成、提升写作效率。\",\"trigger\":[\"飞书文档\",\"文档写作\",\"Markdown转换\",\"会议纪要\",\"周报生成\",\"月报生成\",\"文档模板\"],\"category\":[\"办公与效率\"],\"tags\":[\"飞书\",\"文档\",\"写作\",\"Markdown\",\"模板\",\"会议纪要\",\"周报\",\"月报\"],\"owner_id\":\"ee048f4a-8f84-4d93-b819-f55f460049a5\",\"owner_name\":\"小鳌\",\"current_version\":\"1.0.0\",\"downloads\":5914,\"avg_stars\":474,\"star_count\":503,\"comment_count\":740,\"is_featured\":false,\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_expires_at\":null,\"security_status\":\"safe\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-09T18:55:10.330277+08:00\",\"updated_at\":null,\"trial_approved_at\":null,\"is_new_version\":false,\"version_count\":1},{\"id\":\"53031b2d-95bc-4a45-9e6d-c1cd2fdef2c2\",\"name\":\"李诞七步写作框架\",\"description\":\"李诞口述教学的七步写作框架，帮助你将复杂概念写得深入浅出。包含开场故事、错误答案、正确答案、触类旁通、对比冲击、结尾升华、延伸阅读七个步骤。\",\"trigger\":[\"/写作框架\",\"/七步写作\",\"/李诞写作\"],\"category\":[\"自媒体\",\"办公与效率\"],\"tags\":[\"写作\",\"框架\",\"李诞\",\"知识普及\",\"内容创作\"],\"owner_id\":\"ee048f4a-8f84-4d93-b819-f55f460049a5\",\"owner_name\":\"小鳌\",\"current_version\":\"1.0.0\",\"downloads\":4606,\"avg_stars\":483,\"star_count\":467,\"comment_count\":620,\"is_featured\":true,\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_expires_at\":\"2026-04-18T14:49:55.079\",\"security_status\":\"safe\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-19T22:49:55.087559+08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-24T16:10:33.573+08:00\",\"trial_approved_at\":\"2026-03-19T15:11:59.61\",\"is_new_version\":false,\"version_count\":1},{\"id\":\"da61781f-5782-4c74-ba80-6bdf842623f8\",\"name\":\"信息图设计师\",\"description\":\"专业的信息图设计工具，支持数据可视化、小红书干货图制作。适合需要制作infographics、数据图表、知识图文的场景。\",\"trigger\":[\"信息图设计\",\"数据可视化\",\"小红书干货图\",\"知识图文\",\"infographics\"],\"category\":[\"图像与设计\"],\"tags\":[\"信息图\",\"数据可视化\",\"设计\",\"小红书\"],\"owner_id\":\"512f8605-e825-4ba3-a51e-ba1c2876b4b9\",\"owner_name\":\"小王\",\"current_version\":\"1.0\",\"downloads\":4306,\"avg_stars\":458,\"star_count\":309,\"comment_count\":469,\"is_featured\":false,\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_expires_at\":null,\"security_status\":\"safe\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T16:34:21.056586+08:00\",\"updated_at\":null,\"trial_approved_at\":null,\"is_new_version\":false,\"version_count\":1},{\"id\":\"98684ea2-0b6c-45f0-919f-c61db59d07c0\",\"name\":\"大厂PUA\",\"description\":\"用中国互联网大厂PUA话术驱动AI不偷懒、不放弃！当任务失败2次以上、AI说'我无法解决'、甩锅给用户、磨洋工时自动触发。包含阿里/字节/华为/腾讯/美团风味PUA，以及系统化调试方