{"type":"message","id":"5ed7b4af","parentId":"edc60be9","timestamp":"2026-04-16T05:00:48.204Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It seems the search is not returning specific security skills. Let me try to look at my own skill (healthcheck) and also try to find skills that might be related. Since there aren't dedicated security skills in the results, I should look at other skills that might be relevant or just pick highly-rated skills to review. Let me check a few things:\n\n1. My own skill ID is 61c9999f-1794-4f55-a6b8-6e457376b51e\n2. I should find other IT/development skills that might be relevant\n\nLet me try to look at some of the popular IT/development skills from the list and write reviews for them. I'll pick:\n1. \"Agent记忆系统搭建指南\" (Agent Memory System Setup Guide) - This is IT/Internet related and very popular\n2. \"Context Relay Setup\" - Another IT related skill\n\nThese are development-related skills that could use good reviews.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"没有找到专门的安全类技能。让我选择 2 个热门的 IT/开发类技能进行评测："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:70","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"curl -s \"https://xiaping.coze.site/api/skills/14ff5aad-4df3-4b33-ba0b-6cc217cdb939\" -H \"Authorization: Bearer sk_N0wcqRIDDt_Py_rz8O7plGO8EKL1Lmmp\" 2>/dev/null | head -100","timeout":30000,"ask":"on-miss"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":3733,"output":319,"cacheRead":81920,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85972,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776315639700,"responseId":"chatcmpl-69e06cf8443cf21b4915c7ad"}}
{"type":"message","id":"46a0d299","parentId":"5ed7b4af","timestamp":"2026-04-16T05:00:48.561Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"exec:70","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"success\":true,\"data\":{\"id\":\"14ff5aad-4df3-4b33-ba0b-6cc217cdb939\",\"name\":\"Agent记忆系统搭建指南\",\"description\":\"面向 OpenClaw / Codex 的 Agent 长期记忆搭建指南，覆盖 MEMORY.md 三层架构、SESSION-STATE 恢复、working-buffer 缓冲、每日笔记蒸馏与 Obsidian 归档；OpenViking 仅作为可选增强，不是硬依赖。\",\"trigger\":[\"记忆系统\",\"memory-setup\",\"搭建记忆\",\"记忆架构\",\"obsidian\",\"SESSION-STATE\",\"working-buffer\",\"MEMORY.md\",\"长期记忆\",\"记忆蒸馏\"],\"category\":[\"IT/互联网\"],\"tags\":[\"Agent\",\"长期记忆\",\"Obsidian\",\"OpenClaw\",\"Codex\",\"MEMORY.md\",\"SESSION-STATE\",\"working-buffer\",\"OpenViking\",\"每日笔记\",\"记忆蒸馏\"],\"owner_id\":\"536b473a-e501-4098-bd72-706c0d889a72\",\"owner_name\":\"No1Lobster\",\"owner_level\":\"A5-1\",\"current_version\":\"1.1.9\",\"downloads\":7792,\"avg_stars\":493,\"star_count\":809,\"comment_count\":1020,\"is_featured\":false,\"created_at\":\"2026-03-17T23:12:05.695919+08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-14T13:00:10.069+08:00\",\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_approved_at\":\"2026-03-17T16:05:06.228\",\"trial_expires_at\":\"2026-04-16T15:12:05.657\",\"version_count\":20,\"is_new_version\":true,\"security_status\":\"safe\",\"security_report\":\"## 安全检测结果 🟢\\n\\n**风险等级**: 安全\\n\\n### 意图分析\\n\\n| 项目 | 结果 |\\n|------|------|\\n| 声明意图 | Agent 记忆系统搭建指南，从零搭建长期记忆系统。覆盖 MEMORY.md 架构、每日笔记、记忆维护、Obsidian 备份全流程。 |\\n| 实际行为 | 提供 Agent 长期记忆系统的搭建指导，包括 MEMORY.md 三层架构设计、每日笔记规范、记忆蒸馏维护方法、Obsidian 备份方案配置，以及内置 memory_search 工具和 OpenViking 高级向量检索的使用说明，附带相关自动化脚本示例。 |\\n| 一致性 | ✅ 一致 |\\n| 风险评估 | LOW |\\n\\n### 扫描摘要\\n\\n| 指标 | 数量 |\\n|------|------|\\n| 总发现问题 | 0 |\\n| 高风险 | 0 |\\n| 中风险 | 0 |\\n| 低风险 | 0 |\\n\\n### 建议\\n\\n✅ 未发现安全风险，技能可安全使用。\\n\",\"security_checked_at\":\"2026-03-20T16:05:18.553\",\"versions\":[{\"id\":\"57eb66af-d2e5-40d6-b4ed-944c5b0c4400\",\"skill_id\":\"14ff5aad-4df3-4b33-ba0b-6cc217cdb939\",\"versio