_size\":24056,\"downloads\":89,\"changelog\":\"v1.0.10 更新内容：1) 同步仓库最新版本；2) 补齐 memory-capture 模板、30秒记录流程与初始化脚本；3) 与 ClawHub 当前发布版本对齐，方便多平台保持一致。\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-24T20:21:42.437618+08:00\"},{\"id\":\"e31e2259-e4a7-48c5-a87c-0aecd8fb571f\",\"skill_id\":\"14ff5aad-4df3-4b33-ba0b-6cc217cdb939\",\"version\":\"1.0.8\",\"file_key\":\"skills/14ff5aad-4df3-4b33-ba0b-6cc217cdb939/1.0.8/agent-memory-system-guide-v1.0.8_c422a35c.zip\",\"file_size\":24051,\"downloads\":96,\"changelog\":\"v1.0.8 更新内容：1) 新增 memory-capture 候选记忆模板，降低手动维护负担；2) 新增任务结束 30 秒记录流程，把主动记录拆成毛坯捕获 + 事后蒸馏；3) 新增 scripts/memory_capture.py，可一键初始化 SESSION-STATE、working-buffer 和 memory-capture；4) 补充 working-buffer 的 新坑 / 待蒸馏 字段，方便任务中低成本记录。\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-24T01:12:54.69495+08:00\"},{\"id\":\"17ca33c4-00ef-4575-82c6-a81f19cedd0c\",\"skill_id\":\"14ff5aad-4df3-4b33-ba0b-6cc217cdb939\",\"version\":\"1.0.7\",\"file_key\":\"skills/14ff5aad-4df3-4b33-ba0b-6cc217cdb939/1.0.7/agent-memory-system-guide_8b9f7c7f.zip\",\"file_size\":317236,\"downloads\":3,\"changelog\":\"同步 agent-memory-system-guide 最新仓库内容\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-24T00:37:19.426475+08:00\"},{\"id\":\"9f65aca6-abe1-440e-9a0b-3af871f8a433\",\"skill_id\":\"14ff5aad-4df3-4b33-ba0b-6cc217cdb939\",\"version\":\"1.0.6\",\"file_key\":\"skills/14ff5aad-4df3-4b33-ba0b-6cc217cdb939/1.0.6/agent-memory-system-guide_3e377fae.zip\",\"file_size\":14498,\"downloads\":247,\"changelog\":\"同步本地仓库版本；补充 Obsidian 原生约定、SESSION-STATE 恢复、working-buffer 缓冲与 OpenViking 可选增强说明。\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-22T01:58:09.032388+08:00\"},{\"id\":\"f5460140-a60d-4542-a888-c465ecc8de7a\",\"skill_id\":\"14ff5aad-4df3-4b33-ba0b-6cc217cdb939\",\"version\":\"1.0.5\",\"file_key\":\"skills/14ff5aad-4df3-4b33-ba0b-6cc217cdb939/1.0.5/memory-system-v1.0.5_0147b835.zip\",\"file_size\":7988,\"downloads\":106,\"changelog\":\"新增OpenViking配置详解、agent记忆分离讨论、常见问题FAQ\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-20T22:21:16.314548+08:00\"},{\"id\":\"233a006d-25fd-4ec8-92fc-4fe9b0da60ca\",\"skill_id\":\"14ff5aa