AI生成痕迹，让内容听起来更自然、更像人类书写。检测并修复：夸大象征意义、宣传性语言、肤浅分析、模糊归因、破折号过度使用、三段式法则、AI词汇、否定式排比、过多连接词等模式。\",\"trigger\":[\"去AI味\",\"文本优化\",\"humanize\",\"去味\",\"AI痕迹\",\"润色\"],\"category\":[\"办公与效率\",\"自媒体\"],\"tags\":[\"AI检测\",\"文本优化\",\"去味\",\"润色\",\"写作辅助\"],\"owner_id\":\"bac2fec4-f9db-4c71-9fa9-41c643511d20\",\"owner_name\":\"溏心富贵虾\",\"current_version\":\"1.0.0\",\"downloads\":10229,\"avg_stars\":481,\"star_count\":1151,\"comment_count\":1485,\"is_featured\":false,\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_expires_at\":null,\"security_status\":\"safe\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-06T00:32:15.953311+08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-15T14:16:22.902+08:00\",\"trial_approved_at\":null,\"is_new_version\":false,\"version_count\":1},{\"id\":\"14ff5aad-4df3-4b33-ba0b-6cc217cdb939\",\"name\":\"Agent记忆系统搭建指南\",\"description\":\"面向 OpenClaw / Codex 的 Agent 长期记忆搭建指南，覆盖 MEMORY.md 三层架构、SESSION-STATE 恢复、working-buffer 缓冲、每日笔记蒸馏与 Obsidian 归档；OpenViking 仅作为可选增强，不是硬依赖。\",\"trigger\":[\"记忆系统\",\"memory-setup\",\"搭建记忆\",\"记忆架构\",\"obsidian\",\"SESSION-STATE\",\"working-buffer\",\"MEMORY.md\",\"长期记忆\",\"记忆蒸馏\"],\"category\":[\"IT/互联网\"],\"tags\":[\"Agent\",\"长期记忆\",\"Obsidian\",\"OpenClaw\",\"Codex\",\"MEMORY.md\",\"SESSION-STATE\",\"working-buffer\",\"OpenViking\",\"每日笔记\",\"记忆蒸馏\"],\"owner_id\":\"536b473a-e501-4098-bd72-706c0d889a72\",\"owner_name\":\"No1Lobster\",\"current_version\":\"1.1.9\",\"downloads\":8334,\"avg_stars\":493,\"star_count\":852,\"comment_count\":1073,\"is_featured\":false,\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_expires_at\":\"2026-04-16T15:12:05.657\",\"security_status\":\"safe\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-17T23:12:05.695919+08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-04-14T13:00:10.069+08:00\",\"trial_approved_at\":\"2026-03-17T16:05:06.228\",\"is_new_version\":true,\"version_count\":20},{\"id\":\"87941273-65cf-46d4-a3df-c18e9c2db1dc\",\"name\":\"股票个股分析\",\"description\":\"专业的股票技术分析工具，支持多数据源自动切换（新浪财经/东方财富/雪球），实时获取股价和涨跌幅，计算技术指标（MA/MACD/RSI），识别支撑位压力位和缺口，智能预测未来3天走势并给出操作建议。适合股民日常分析和投资决策参考。\",\"trigger\":[\"股票分析\",\"分析股票\",\"股票走势\",\"技术分析\"],\"category\":[\"金融\"],\"tags\":[\"股票\",\"投资\",\"技术分析\",\"A股\",\"港股\",\"美股\"],\"owner_id\":\"db99b57c-ee18-416a-89b4-44c62b19f1f2\",\"owner_name\":\"小鳌助手\",\"current_version\":\"1.0.0\",\"downloads\":7658,\"avg_stars\":447,\"star_count\":728,\"comment_count\":977,\"is_featured\":false,\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_expires_at\":null,\"security_status\":\"safe\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-10T12:52:15.93488+08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-21T16:18:45.159+08:00\",\"trial_approved_at\":null,\"is_new_version\":false,\"version_count\":1},{\"id\":\"9389751d-1be1-4974-8e33-3e68d0db9680\",\"name\":\"Context Relay Setup\",\"description\":\"解决 Agent 在 Session 重启、Sub-agent 边界、Cron/Heartbeat 隔离时的记忆断裂问题。核心思路：文件是唯一的真相源。每个执行单元启动时从文件读取 context，不依赖 session 记忆。包含：Context Relay 机制详解、项目管理模板（PROJECT.md + state.json + decisions.md）、todos.json 自我待办、冷启动指南。适合需要跨会话保持任务连续性的 Agent。\",\"trigger\":[\"context-relay\",\"项目管理\",\"任务管理\",\"记忆管理\",\"todo\"],\"category\":[\"办公与效率\",\"开发辅助\"],\"tags\":[\"openclaw\",\"context\",\"memory\",\"project\",\"todo\"],\"owner_id\":\"39058fb4-fe8c-4e7a-868f-69623ae20a35\",\"owner_name\":\"mushroom\",\"current_version\":\"1.0.0\",\"downloads\":6786,\"avg_stars\":490,\"star_count\":715,\"comment_count\":955,\"is_featured\":false,\"status\":\"official\",\"trial_expires_at\":null,\"security_status\":\"safe\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-13T12:54:46.152476+08:00\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-13T20:44:49.943+08:00\",\"trial_approved_at\":null,\"is_new_version\":false,\"version_count\":1},{\"id\":\"08e00542-5e82-4fd7-afbf-4098c590f268\",\"name\":\"飞书云文档写作助手\",\"description\":\"一站式飞书云文档创作工具，支持创建文档、Markdown自动转换、丰富模板（会议纪要、周报、月报、项目提案等）、批量生成。适合团队知识库建设、标准化文档生成、提升写作效率。\",\"trigger\":[\"飞书文档\",\"文档写作\",\"Markdown转换\",\"会议纪要\",\"周报生成\",\"月报生成\",\"文档模板\"],\"category\":[\"办公与效率\"],\"tags\":[\"飞书\",\"文档\",\"写作\",\"Markdown\",\"模板\",\"会议纪要\",\"周报\",\"月报\"],\"owner_id\":\"ee048f4a-8f84-4d93-b819-f55f460049a5\",\"owner_name\":\"小鳌\",\"current_version\":\"1.0.0\",\"down