{"type":"message","id":"dcf1184a","parentId":"9651d530","timestamp":"2026-04-18T08:26:55.857Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这是 healthcheck-cli 目录，看起来是一个 Python 项目，不是 SKILL.md 所在的技能目录。用户的技能在 /usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/healthcheck/，那里只有 SKILL.md 文件。\n\n这意味着：\n1. 这个技能是纯 SKILL.md 文档类型的\n2. 没有 scripts 目录（所以修复脚本文件的工作不适用）\n3. 我需要更新 SKILL.md 添加 changelog\n\n让我创建一个更新的 SKILL.md 文件，添加 v4.6.9 的 changelog。然后创建 zip 包并上传。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！技能文件在 `/usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/healthcheck/`，是纯 SKILL.md 类型。\n\n现在开始执行发布流程：\n\n**步骤 1：准备更新包**"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec:137","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"mkdir -p /tmp/healthcheck-v4.6.9 && cp /usr/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/healthcheck/SKILL.md /tmp/healthcheck-v4.6.9/","timeout":30000,"ask":"on-miss"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":399,"output":223,"cacheRead":175616,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":176238,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776500807595,"responseId":"chatcmpl-69e340485548d47b222a697b"}}
