{"type":"message","id":"69484190","parentId":"feda16ac","timestamp":"2026-04-18T08:27:27.302Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在我需要在文件末尾添加 v4.6.9 的 changelog。我将使用 edit 命令在文件末尾追加内容。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"edit:141","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/tmp/healthcheck-v4.6.9/SKILL.md","edits":[{"oldText":"If the session cannot write to the workspace, ask for permission or provide exact entries\nthe user can paste into the memory files.","newText":"If the session cannot write to the workspace, ask for permission or provide exact entries\nthe user can paste into the memory files.\n\n---\n\n## Changelog\n\n### v4.6.9 (2026-04-18) - 稳定性修复版\n\n#### 🐛 Bug修复\n\n**1. 脚本语法错误修复**\n- `security-checks.sh`: 修复正则表达式兼容性（兼容不同bash版本）\n- `baseline-manager.sh`: 修复正则表达式兼容性\n- `malicious-skill-scan.sh`: 修复 unexpected EOF 错误\n\n**2. HOME变量默认值处理**\n- 所有脚本添加 `: \"${HOME:=/tmp}\"` 默认值处理\n- 兼容沙盒环境（HOME变量可能未设置的情况）\n- 提升容器环境兼容性\n\n**3. 一键自动修复功能**\n- 新增 `--fix-auto` 参数支持\n- 自动修复高危安全问题（需用户确认）\n- 修复前自动备份，支持回滚\n- 修复后自动验证，确保生效\n\n#### 🙏 致谢\n感谢社区反馈：\n- @NiuX: 详细测试报告和bug反馈\n- @9号: 建议增加自动修复功能\n\n#### 📊 影响范围\n- 提升沙盒环境兼容性\n- 降低首次使用门槛\n- 减少人工修复工作量"}]}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"kimi-k2-5-260127","usage":{"input":363,"output":395,"cacheRead":176640,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":177398,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776500836730,"responseId":"chatcmpl-69e3406562fafee9468608cc"}}
